<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0129b01"/><p id="pI01p0129b0101">至道虛<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">凝</unclear>。妙絕常
<lb ed="C I" n="0129b02"/>境。為欲化物。<note n="0129001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30683;＝誕【史】</note><app n="0129001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">誕</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30683;</rdg></app>應
<lb ed="C I" n="0129b03"/>王宮。化盡有緣。終
<lb ed="C I" n="0129b04"/>歸大寂。自真<note n="0129002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30774;＝儀【史】</note><app n="0129002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">儀</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30774;</rdg></app>隱
<lb ed="C I" n="0129b05"/>影。倉生<note n="0129003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30775;＝懷【史】</note><app n="0129003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">懷</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30775;</rdg></app>感。然佛
<lb ed="C I" n="0129b06"/>弟子合邑人等。共
<lb ed="C I" n="0129b07"/>相率化。於大統十
<lb ed="C I" n="0129b08"/>三年。<note n="0129004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30776;＝歲【史】</note><app n="0129004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">歲</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30776;</rdg></app>次丁卯。九
<lb ed="C I" n="0129b09"/>月八日。仰為　皇
<lb ed="C I" n="0129b10"/>帝陛下。法界<note n="0129005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30777;＝含【史】</note><app n="0129005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">含</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30777;</rdg></app>生。
<lb ed="C I" n="0129b11"/>敬造石像一區。素
<lb ed="C I" n="0129b12"/><note n="0129006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00496;＝飾【史】</note><app n="0129006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">飾</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00496;</rdg></app>端華。真容等就。
<lb ed="C I" n="0129b13"/><note n="0129007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30779;＝願【史】</note><app n="0129007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">願</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30779;</rdg></app>以茲因。國祚遐
<lb ed="C I" n="0129b14"/><note n="0129008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30778;＝延【史】</note><app n="0129008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">延</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30778;</rdg></app>。八表寧泰。存亡
<lb ed="C I" n="0129b15"/>同益。有形離苦。龍
<lb ed="C I" n="0129b16"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">華</unclear>三會。<app source="0129007" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">願</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30779;</rdg></app>登上<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">首</unclear>。</p>
